
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-secheverria-ace-client-disadvantaged-00.txt'>
    <title>"ACE Clients in Disadvantaged Networks", Sebastian Echeverria, Ludwig Seitz, Dan Klinedinst, Grace Lewis</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-secheverria-ace-client-disadvantaged-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes a set of recommendations to use when implementing ACE/OAuth 2.0 clients that are working in disadvantaged networks.  Issues such as token revocation have a much higher priority in scenarios where Resource Servers are IoT devices, and network connectivity is limited and intermittent.</description>
    <dc:date>2019-03-08T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
